title: 09/23: Weekend Recap - Falcons Up, Packers Down? (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Getting you started with winners (1:40) and losers (6:24) from Week 3. Winners include Matt Ryan and Tyler Boyd. Losers include Jamaal Williams and every SF pass catcher which of course leads us to the big NFL news items you need to know about (16:00) and our reaction to Jimmy Garoppolo's injury ... How concerned are we about the GB offense (22:48)? Should you be looking to sell? Then let's look at the Week 3 leaders at QB (27:05), RB (32:00), WR (36:36) and TE (39:40) and talk about the MegaDuds (40:44) like Derrick Henry and Kenyan Drake ... Recapping every game (46:02) with Fantasy takes and rest of season rankings ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
